ties\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Look at their seminaries-turned-ghost-towns, testament to aggiornamento gone awry.\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A recent Order of nuns called a festive dinner to celebrate the announcement of their demise.\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, you say, but wasn't there the American bishop who registered a gentle reservation?\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3398, \"end\": 3406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999995919866629, \"rank\": 4.040032957240756e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, true enough.\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But his gray suit and Roman collar seemed to dilute the effect.\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3491, \"end\": 3503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clerical_collar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roman collar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clerical_collar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clerical_collar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Call me old fashioned, but a priest in a gray suit does not make hearts race as does the sight of St. Francis Xavier in cassock holding high the cross.\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read the Whole Article  Copyright \\u00a9Lifesite News\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3734, \"entities\": []}]}"